{"tid":600266,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Atari 正式發表懷舊主題新主機「Atari VCS」 經典搖桿控制器同步登場","createTime":"2018-03-21T07:12:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-21T08:23:36.000Z","uid":42675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"def0724fa8d22fd4a0331a16dda69715cb76e410","tid":600266,"uid":42675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T07:12:15.000Z","msg":"美國老牌遊戲廠商 Atari，配合 19 日開幕的 2018 年遊戲開發者論壇（GDC 2018）正式發表旗下遊戲主機新產品「Atari VCS」，預定 4 月起開始接受預訂，上市日期與價格目前還未公布。<br />\n <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/21/150940_fa63fcaedf609188d03a584e59adaa5b.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F21%2F150940_fa63fcaedf609188d03a584e59adaa5b.JPG&h=01443b8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n官方同時公布了搭配 Atari VCS 的控制器，包括符合現今主流設計的「摩登控制器（Modern Controller）」以及依照當年 Atari 2600 搖桿設計的「經典搖桿（Classic Joystick）」兩種。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/21/151058_fa63fcaedf609188d03a584e59adaa5b.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F21%2F151058_fa63fcaedf609188d03a584e59adaa5b.JPG&h=b53250ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/21/151109_fa63fcaedf609188d03a584e59adaa5b.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F21%2F151109_fa63fcaedf609188d03a584e59adaa5b.JPG&h=527aab20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/21/151113_fa63fcaedf609188d03a584e59adaa5b.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F21%2F151113_fa63fcaedf609188d03a584e59adaa5b.JPG&h=d56594c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/21/151121_fa63fcaedf609188d03a584e59adaa5b.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2